name: Phil Batisto
text: The location on Zumbehl is permanently closed. But it Was good.

name: Jyve Turkey
text: Clean and quiet, I went when they had a promo for free pizza. I really enjoyed it, you have to cook it yourself but it's as easy as tossing in the oven.

name: Monica K
text: They have good pizza here. The staff have always been friendly and quick. Never had any issues here, but I would not recommend ordering any crust with extra butter. This plaza has lots of stores crammed into this area, so parking nearby can be a challenge sometimes.

name: jenn burkhardt
text: Very helpful and friendly staff working. Had never tried their pizza before, and they had explained everything to us! Took it home, followed their directions and voila, delicious take out pizza! Will definitely go back again!

name: Krysta Lemm
text: Good food that's easy for a family on a busy night!  The staff was less than energetic and hardly made eye contact, but everything came out good.

name: Karl Rickard
text: Just had Papa Murphy's for the first time today.  Ordered 4 large pies, including their vegetarian, stuffed Chicago Style, Mediterranean Chicken, and a plain cheese.  They were ready in minutes, and looked great.  I had my doubts about how they would turn out in my own oven, but they cooked to perfection.  Will be going back!

name: Cathy Niehaus
text: They are closing the St Charles location which makes me sad. I love the pizza choices

name: kasey bross
text: This location was closer to where I was running errands. I hadn't been to any in about a year bc the last few times were "meh". The Zumbel Rd. Location will now be my go-to. It was fantastic.

name: Megan Covington
text: My family has always loved Papa Murphy's. I love the manager here, she's friendly & always smiling. Great staff and quick service.

name: Hank Bowman
text: Wife ordered 2 pizzas at 4:00 PM for pickup at 5:30 PM. I arrived at 5:30 PM and pizzas are not even made as I type this up on my phone. Slow workers!!

name: Jeremy Schad
text: Always friendly and fast. Call your order ahead for even faster pick-up.

name: Chris Sheppard
text: Love Papa Murphy's pizza and only get it when I am in an area as I dok not have a store close to my home.

name: M Shelton
text: Good stuff if your oven works

name: Steven Troeger
text: Fast,  friendly and delicious!

name: Patricia Usher-McElroy
text: Very good fresh pizza. It's our family's favorite pizza place

name: P Oliver
text: Great location. Never had a problem here.

name: Brian Teglo
text: Good pizza at a good price!

name: Tracy Carlson
text: Love their thin crust and very friendly service!

name: Tim Cardoni
text: Good Take and Bake!

name: Jennifer Melvin
text: Wish our location hadn't closed

name: Abagael Baldwin
text: Location is closed now

name: Steve Brewer
text: Great service and extremely nice staff

name: Debra Desanto
text: Awesome

name: Wanda Thompson
text: Pizza is del6

name: Sam Kelly
text: Fast, friendly, and delicious

name: Velvet Ohlen
text: Pizza is great
